#Growth #Prosperity #Softgirl #Softlife #Purpose

I don’t know about you sis but this year I will have thousands in business funding! So building your business credit is a must..

1. Do not make the mistake of registering your LLC as your first step to starting your business. There’s many steps that must be taken before that which is making sure you have your business address, phone number, professional email, and a professional website. 

2. As good as it sounds, it’s not true! In order to unlock hundreds of thousand in business funding, your personal credit must be decent sis. Work on your personal credit while working in your business credit... yes! You can work on them both at the same time. 

3. Lenders want to see that you’re a professional business. Using your personal address for all of your businesses needs will literally stop you from getting the funding you need to scale your business. It’s 2023, get you a virtual address sis!
Oh and the face card is platinum with no limit.😉
I love on ME, don’t settle, and always invest into myself💋 What am I?

Just because you have bad credit right now doesn’t mean it’s forever.😂 So calm down. You can actually fix your credit relatively fast! I boosted my score by over +180 points in less than 45 days. And I won’t stop until I’m close to 850😚

1. If you’ve dug yourself into a whole of debt, don’t dig deeper! Just because you can afford the payments of something doesn’t mean you can afford it. If you don’t have it to spend in CASH.. don’t buy it! You’ll end up spending more money. 

2. If you don’t know how to dispute items on your credit report, pay a legit credit repair company to fix it monthly. It’s as simple as sending a letter to the credit bureaus. 

3. My favorite! Adding a tradeline can cost you a couple hundred but it’s worth it. Your credit will increase by a lot in less than 45 days. The history stays on your report forever. And if that tradeline has a credit limit… guess what! You also have that same credit limit on your report. The choices you can make with good credit and a high credit limit are endless, just be smart about it and don’t take a risk unless it’s a good one.
